# GitHub Pages Configuration

This repository is configured to work with GitHub Pages.

## Files Structure
```
STT_HEB/
├── index.html          # Main HTML file
├── script.js           # JavaScript functionality
├── style.css           # CSS styling
├── README.md           # Documentation
└── .nojekyll           # Disable Jekyll processing
```

## Deployment Instructions

1. **Upload Files**: Upload all files to your GitHub repository
2. **Enable Pages**:
   - Go to repository Settings
   - Scroll to "Pages" section
   - Select "Deploy from a branch"
   - Choose "main" branch
   - Click "Save"
3. **Access**: Your app will be available at:
   `https://[username].github.io/STT_HEB`

## Requirements
- Modern browser (Chrome, Edge, Safari)
- Microphone access
- Internet connection
- HTTPS (required for microphone access)

## Features
- Hebrew Speech-to-Text
- Real-time transcription
- Multiple language support
- Responsive design
- Keyboard shortcuts
- Continuous recording mode
